song_name: Troubled By The Way We Came Together

version_description: With the use of a capo on 1 fret, the chords Bb, G#, D#, F#, and Dm become A, G, D, F, and C#m.
People always miss the extra two chords in the verse and chorus. The ooh part also is a verse btw. Enjoy :) I am little confused with the E chord. If you have a better idea, tell me.
